.SH INSTALLATION
.SS System-wide installation:
.RS
sudo make install
.RE
.SS User installation:
.RS
make install-user
.RE
.SS Configuration:
.RS
autoterm-backend --setup
.br
source ~/.zshrc
.RE
.SH UNINSTALLATION
.SS System-wide:
.RS
sudo make uninstall
.RE
.SS User installation:
.RS
make uninstall-user
.RE
.SH DEPENDENCIES
.IP \(bu 2
Python 3.7+
.IP \(bu 2
zsh shell
.IP \(bu 2
groq Python package
.IP \(bu 2
Groq API key (free at https://console.groq.com)
.SH TROUBLESHOOTING
.TP
.B API key not found
Run:
.B autoterm-backend --setup
.TP
.B Connection failed
Check your API key and internet connection with:
.B autoterm-backend --test
.TP
.B Double-tab not working
Ensure AutoTerm is sourced in ~/.zshrc:
.br
source /path/to/autoterm.zsh
